Developer Terms of Use
des:
The Amerigroup Skill is a hands-free option to help you find the health care information you need quickly and securely. It’s just one more way Amerigroup is making it easier for you to manage your health.

The information in this skill is provided for informational and educational purposes only. Medical advice is not provided. Always consult your doctor for appropriate examinations, treatment, testing, and care recommendations. In an emergency, dial 911 or visit the nearest emergency room.

When using this skill, your personal financial information may be read aloud and/or displayed in response to commands or requests spoken by you.
